title: MaxTo v2015.11.1.0
description:
MaxTo v2015.11.1.0

The window manager you didn't know you missed
Divide your screen, increase your productivity, made for Windows

Control your windows
Whenever you maximize a window, MaxTo puts that window into a region.

Use awesome keyboard shortcuts
Quickly move windows around using MaxTo's easy to remember keyboard shortcuts.

Made for Windows 10 (Supports W10/8.1/8/7/Vista)
MaxTo works with all versions of Windows since Vista (SP2). It fully supports 64-bit and 32-bit programs, and works well with UAC.

In your language
